{"tid":1088888,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【林鄭女皇帝】大律師公會：逃犯條例修訂後特首成移交程序唯一決定人","createTime":"2019-04-02T11:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T13:43:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c50eb04b625f89432329349555f7439de2383153","tid":1088888,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1450977-20190402.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1450977-20190402.htm&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m64jsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=fcbbaa4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1450977-20190402.htm&h=f2945ffe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1450977-20190402.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1450977_1_L_20190402184125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1450977_1_L_20190402184125.jpg&h=19ab0708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港大律師公會發表聲明，再就《逃犯條例》修例提出意見，指現時逃犯條例不涵蓋內地，並非「漏洞」，而是立法機構在1997年所作的謹慎決定，批評特首、律政司司長和保安局局長，多次形容為「漏洞」的言論，屬於誤導。<br />\n<br />\n公會質疑，經修例後，行政長官會成為移交程序的唯一決定人，無立法會監察下，將無法問責；又指今次修例建議剔除部分經濟罪行，為商人提供一定保障，但似乎是「假象」。"},{"pid":"606d8844255cf8ed9171607eb611520d31bf0e16","tid":1088888,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}